 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/parkway-drive-poppy@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/parkway-drive-poppy@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/parkway-drive-poppy@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>美国狂欢节 (Mayhem Festival) 自 2015 年以来首次宣布回归，并分享了演出阵容 - 了解更多信息如下。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/poppy-shares-madonna-meets-metal-single-new-way-out-and-tells-us-how-theres-plenty-to-be-angry-about-3762126">Poppy 向我们讲述了沉重的新单曲“New Way Out”以及“有很多值得生气的事情”</a></strong></li></ul><p>昨晚（6 月 4 日），Mayhem Festival 在社交媒体上公布了演出阵容，确认了自 2015 年举办最后一场活动以来的回归。 Mayhem 的回归将不是像过去那样举办巡回音乐节，而是一场为期一天的活动定于 10 月 12 日在加利福尼亚州圣贝纳迪诺举行。</p><p>与过去的音乐节不同的是，混乱音乐<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/slayer">节</a>现在将展示由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bad-omens">Bad Omens</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/slipknot">Poppy</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/poppy">等</a>乐队领衔的年轻艺人。</p><p> Mayhem 回归的主角是 Bad Omens，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/parkway-drive">Parkway Drive</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/architects">Architects</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jinjer">Jinjer</a> 、Poppy 等都名列前茅。法案中包括的其他乐队包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kittie">Kittie</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/august-burns-red">August Burns Red</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/we-came-as-romans">We Came As Romans</a> 、Suicide Silence、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hanabie">Hanabie</a> 、Mothica 等。</p><p>混乱音乐节回归的门票尚未开始销售，但粉丝们可以<a href="https://mayhemfest.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">通过音乐节的官方网站注册以抢先体验</a>。</p><h3> <strong>2024 年混乱音乐节的完整阵容是：</strong></h3><p><strong>不祥之兆</strong><br /><strong>百汇大道</strong><br /><strong>建筑师</strong><br /><strong>金杰尔</strong><br /><strong>罂粟</strong><br /><strong>基蒂</strong><br /><strong>奥古斯特·伯恩斯·红</strong><br /><strong>紫罗兰之后七小时</strong><br /><strong>我们作为罗马人而来</strong><br /><strong>自杀沉默</strong><br /><strong>下葬后</strong><br /><strong>丢下</strong><br /><strong>奥西里斯的诞生</strong><br /><strong>莫蒂卡</strong><br /><strong>花比</strong><br /><strong>佩顿帕里什</strong><br /><strong>最黑暗的时刻</strong><br /><strong>挖掘</strong><br /><strong>布鲁图斯</strong><br /><strong>它今天死了</strong><br /><strong>磨练学校</strong><br /><strong>圣战</strong><br /><strong>罗马蜡烛</strong></p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C7zeWjFyqDo/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.1